data.description: Awesome 1.5 story, 4 bedrooms with spacious master on main floor, master bath with jet tub. High ceilings in formal dining room / living room. 2 bedrooms with full bath on 2nd floor. Nicely finished lower level with 2nd family room, office, 4th bedroom with egress window and shower. Updates include furnace (Sept 2020) Portion of driveway replaced March 2021, interior walls/ ext paint 2017, granite in bathrooms, kitchen backsplash, portion of siding replaced 2017, roof 2015, hot water heater 2020, radon mitigation system March 2021.
